'''Joe Robinson''' is an English actor and stuntman born in [[Newcastle-upon-Tyne]] on [[31 May]] [[1927]]. His brother is also a stuntman and actor, [[Doug Robinson]]. The Robinson's were a famous family of wrestlers, Joe's father and grandfather were world champions. Robinson initially embarked on a career in wrestling as 'Tiger Joe Robinson' and won the [[European Heavyweight Championship]] in [[1952]].
